in his absence.

00:15:02.399 --> 00:15:05.259
Kayleigh and Tommy went to live with their
mother and avoided getting abused by their

00:15:05.259 --> 00:15:06.259
father.

00:15:06.259 --> 00:15:08.429
Andrea had remarried and had another baby.

00:15:08.429 --> 00:15:16.410
Lenny had never suffered from any trauma.

00:15:16.410 --> 00:15:23.169
Tommy becomes a valedictorian of his class,
and Kayleigh gets married.

